                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue aims to update Apache ORC dependency to the latest version 1.5.4 released at Dec. 20. (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=12318320&amp;amp;version=12344187&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Release Notes&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
